<style>
  .article_column-image {
    width: 100%;
    height: 320px;
    border-radius: 11px;
  }
  img.article_column-image {
    overflow: hidden;
    object-fit: cover;
    object-position: 50% 50%;
  }
  .article_column-image-border {
    border: 1px solid rgba(60, 31, 27, 0.30);
  }
  .article_column {
      height: max-content;
  }
  .article_column-third {
    width: calc(33.3333334% - 33.3333334px);
  }
  .article_column-half {
    width: calc(50% - 25px);
  }
  .article_column-text-third-top {
    padding-top: 81px;
  }
  @media(max-width: 1450px) {
    .article_column-half {
    width: calc(50% - 15px);
  }
    .article_columns-wrapp {
      gap: 30px;
    }
    .article_column-text-third-top {
      padding-top: 114px;
    }
  }
  @media(max-width: 1250px) {
    .article_column-third {
        width: calc(50% - 15px);
    }
    .article_column-text-third-top {
      padding-top: 81px;
    }
  }
  @media(max-width: 950px) {
    .article_column-text-third-top {
      padding-top: 114px;
    }
  }
  @media(max-width: 750px) {
    .article_column-text-third-top {
      padding-top: 0;
    }
    .article_column-half {
      width: 100%
    }
    .article_column-third {
        width: 100%;
        gap: 30px;
    }
    .article_columns-wrapp {
        gap: 30px;
    }
    .rebranding_container {
        gap: 40px;
    }
    .article_column-text .h3-heading-pp, .article_column-text .h3-heading-ss {
        text-align: center;
    }
  }
  @media(max-width: 450px) {
    .article_column-image {
      height: 250px;
    }
  }
</style>

<div class="rebranding_container block-flex-wrap block-gap-50">
  <div class="rebranding-section-title block-flex-wrap block-gap-15 block-flex-center-center">
    <h2 class="h2-heading-ss">
      What is  
      <span class="h2-heading-pp">
       Hermès authentication?
      </span>
    </h2>
  </div>
  <div class="article_columns-wrapp block-flex-wrap block-gap-50 block-flex-start-start">
    <div class="article_column article_column-half article_column-text-half block-flex-wrap block-gap-30">
      <div class="article_column-text block-flex-wrap block-gap-15 block-flex-center-center">
        <p class="article_column-desc body-text taj w-100">
          Hermès authentication is a meticulous process designed to verify the authenticity of Hermès luxury goods, including handbags, bags, and other leather goods. This service is crucial for ensuring that the Hermès item you own or are considering purchasing is genuine and not a counterfeit. Hermès authentication services involve a comprehensive examination of the product’s materials, craftsmanship, and distinctive features, such as the blind stamp and authenticity cards, to determine its authenticity. 
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="article_column article_column-half article_column-text-half block-flex-wrap block-gap-30">
      <div class="article_column-text block-flex-wrap block-gap-15 block-flex-center-center">
        <p class="article_column-desc body-text taj w-100">
          These services are provided by independent experts who possess extensive knowledge and experience in authenticating Hermès items. By leveraging their expertise, these professionals can accurately assess the authenticity of your Hermès products, giving you peace of mind and confidence in your purchase.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

{% schema %}
  {
    "name": "Three text columns",
    "class": "article_columns article_three-columns article_three-text-columns",
    "settings": []
  }
{% endschema %}